reviewText: Amazon, I love this site! This video arrived in fast order and in the condition advertized. Am so glad you had it available. Thank you!!
My daughter loves Wilbur but the older videos are not nearly as good as the new ones on TLC. It's entertaining though.
The Wilbur tapes are the best ones I have found for the 1-3 age range.  My daughter was Crazy for Wilbur.  It's an adorable video and she learned alot from it.

Our 2 year old can't get enough of Wilbur! The playful, silly songs are developmentally appropriate and fun! This video is ideal for 2's since their vocabulary is expanding by the day. We rented Wilbur over and over  from the library and finally decided to purchase it for our home library.
